Name: Outlook Mail - Send an Email
Description: Send an email using Outlook
Params: recipient: Email address of the recipient
Params: subject: Subject of the email
Params: body: Body of the email
Share Tools: github.com/gptscript-ai/tools/apis/outlook/mail/manage
Type: input

#!/bin/bash

cat << EOF

Use the Outlook tools to send an email to the address ${RECIPIENT} with the subject "${SUBJECT}" and the body "${BODY}".

EOF
